      Guidance
    </p>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Approach to financial services legislation under the EU (Withdrawal) Act 2018
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This publication sets out HM Treasury’s approach to laying financial services statutory instruments under the EU (Withdrawal) Act 2018.</p>

  </div>
</div>

